=======================================
After runnig 
enable ssh by following command 
nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config 
edit to make (PermitRootLogin  yes) then ctrl+s to save  ctrl+x to exit 
updating (apt update  then apt upgrade )

========================================
DOCKER INSTALL
========================================
apt install curl

curl -fsSL https://get.docker.com | sh

test installation 
docker run --rm -it hello-world 
=========================================
TAILSCALE INSTALL
=========================================
Firest turn of the lxc 
then from node shell do the following 
nano nano /etc/pve/lxc/(1000).conf    (put lxc CTID that you want instal tailscail)

add the following 2 lines to the file and save and exit

lxc.cgroup2.devices.allow: c 10:200 rwm
lxc.mount.entry: /dev/net/tun dev/net/tun none bind,create=file

Second 
curl -fsSL https://tailscale.com/install.sh | sh
=========================================
then wayes to start it 

tailscale up
tailscale up --advertise-routes=0.0.0.0/24 --advertise-exit-node --ssh
then take the tailscale url and activate it 
